\id JER Matupi Chin Standard Bible 
\h JEREMIAH 
\toc1 JEREMIAH 
\toc2 Jeremiah 
\toc3 Jer 
\mt1 JEREMIAH  
\mt2 (The Book of the Prophet Jeremiah)  
\is1 Jeremiah Cabu Kawng  
\im Jeremiah dongah olphong, amah kawng, khokhuen, olthui boeih thum. He cabu he amah khokhuen kah aka thoeng hno dongkah te a thuicaih. A boel 36 hil he tah cabu he metla a culuinah ti te a thui. Pathen olthang thui ham la cadong ca a khuenah kawng te bitbit tueng. Jeremiah loh a hutnah te a doe tih Pathen kah uepom puencawn la naeh. Jeremiah loh a bibi he 627 \sc b.c.\sc* ah a tong tih 586 \sc b.c.\sc* hil phat a bi. Te vaengah Jerusalem te Babylon loh a loh coeng. Pathen tonghma la a om khuiah pilnam te Pathen taengah uepom la om ham a hoe, Judah te a rhalrhing sak. Pathen taeng lamkah aka hnukpoh Judah rhoek taengah oltak a thui dongah Jeremiah te a hnaemtaek uh. Anih te boekoek la a poek uh dongah a phaep uh, thong a hlak, a khoh uh, a boh uh phoeiah a ram lamloh a haek uh. Jeremiah loh tamna la aka cet pilnam taengah ngaiuepnah a thui, Israel neh Judah hamla olkhueh paipi thai a paek.  
\ib  
